1
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:12,760
Sister, why are you up so late?

2
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,920
You look like a mess.

3
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:15,570
Are you trying to be a ghost?

4
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:19,170
Do you need money again?

5
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:21,280
Didn't I just give you silver this morning?

6
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,280
It's all gone.

7
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:28,800
Then help me get rid of this nuisance.

8
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:34,280
Who are you?

9
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:35,960
Song Xuan.

10
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:39,440
You're the Miss Song who's engaged to my brother.

11
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:41,479
I heard your martial arts are good.

12
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,400
Let's spar.

13
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,240
Brother.

14
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:54,440
Miss Bai, this is a small token of my regard.

15
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,960
That's very kind of you.

16
00:01:58,680 --> 00:02:01,440
Brother, Sister-in-law, you two chat.

17
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,340
I'll go back to my room to rest.

18
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:09,880
Good luck.

19
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,010
Sister, you really sway with the wind.

20
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,280
Sister.

21
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:19,040
Miss Song, if you marry me,

22
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:21,800
you must have heard a lot of rumors.

23
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:23,840
Since I've decided to marry you,

24
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,570
I certainly won't despise you.

25
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:27,760
Sister.

26
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:27,760
Miss Song,

27
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:30,840
marriage should at least be mutual.

28
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,440
And you have no feelings for me.

29
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:38,040
How do you know I have no feelings for you?

30
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,840
I will definitely find out the truth.

31
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,570
To comfort the spirits of the Song Army in heaven.

32
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,880
Miss Song.

33
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:59,160
I am Bai Manchuan,

34
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:02,000
the most notorious wastrel in the capital.

35
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:06,960
Why hang yourself on a crooked tree like me?

36
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,400
Just show up at the wedding on time.

37
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,880
Are you out of your mind?

38
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,280
Hello, Auntie.

39
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,760
Hello, Uncle Zhao.

40
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,820
Hello, Grandpa Li.

41
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,480
Hello, everyone else.

42
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,680
Manchuan, Manchuan.

43
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,960
I had no choice but to come and beg you.

44
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,650
It's my good-for-nothing Xiaohu.

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,360
He had a lapse in judgment.

46
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,200
He was dragged to Linglong Pavilion to gamble.

47
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,720
He not only lost everything,

48
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:37,440
but they've also detained him.

49
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:40,640
They say he has to pay with his life.

50
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,840
Afu, hurry up and take money to redeem him.

51
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,880
Young Master, I already went there with silver.

52
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,880
But the dealer there, Ji Ruyu, said,

53
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:47,840
What did she say?

54
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:49,240
She said her rule is,

55
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,440
that only someone who beats her earns the right to ask for a person.

56
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:55,400
It seems I, Bai Manchuan, the King of Gamblers, must make a comeback.

57
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,800
Young Master.

58
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,320
I see a dark omen on your face.

59
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,720
You are walking into a death trap.

60
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:16,720
If you engage in a life-or-death gamble today, you will surely lose.

61
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,320
I'm taking the boy.

62
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:28,480
Name your terms.

63
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,680
Young Master Bai.

64
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,800
If you can, within the time it takes an incense stick to burn,

65
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,040
solve my puzzle,

66
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,250
you may naturally take him.

67
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,800
And if I can't?

68
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,800
If Young Master Bai fails,

69
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,480
I will still do you a favor.

70
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:47,280
You'll just need to pay ten thousand taels.

71
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:51,400
Boss Ji, that's daylight robbery.

72
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,200
True.

73
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,000
He is just a servant, after all.

74
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,600
Done.

75
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,320
Young Master Bai is indeed extraordinary.

76
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,960
You are so sharp with numbers.

77
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:17,960
If only you applied it elsewhere...

78
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,760
Since I've won,

79
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:22,320
I'll be taking him now.

80
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,850
Young Master Bai, please wait.

81
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:29,080
Young Master Bai, since you're so skilled,

82
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:33,260
are you interested in a high-stakes bet with me?

83
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:34,159
Sure.

84
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:35,760
Let's hear it.

85
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:40,600
No one has ever beaten me in this game.

86
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,810
I'll bet my entire Linglong Pavilion.

87
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:45,960
If you win,

88
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:50,120
you can take all the gold and treasures here.

89
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,000
But what if you lose, Young Master Bai?

90
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,400
I only ask for one condition.

91
00:05:53,400 --> 00:05:55,280
Bet with her! Bet with her!

92
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,920
Bet with her! Bet with her! Bet with her!

93
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,440
Young Master, don't!

94
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,650
Not interested.

95
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:02,280
I'm going home to eat.

96
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,360
Young Master Bai.

97
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:07,000
I have a secret about Miss Song Xuan.

98
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,130
What secret could that 'Daylily' possibly have?

99
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,760
In this capital,

100
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,440
so many men want to marry Miss Song Xuan.

101
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:18,480
Why did she choose your Zhongyi Marquis Manor?

102
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,640
What do you mean?

103
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:23,500
So, Young Master Bai, you're willing to bet now?

104
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,880
Since you've put it that way,

105
00:06:26,760 --> 00:06:28,160
I'm definitely betting.

106
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,040
Miss.

107
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,720
Bad news, Miss.

108
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,960
Young Master Bai went to the gambling house.

109
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:37,760
He's about to gamble with the 'Flower Hand' Gambling Queen, Ji Ruyu.

110
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,250
Then I'll go have a look too.

111
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,480
Miss!

112
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,520
Come out!

113
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,330
Let's go.

114
00:06:58,760 --> 00:06:59,760
Young Master Bai.

115
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,520
We each pick one of these female slaves.

116
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,880
They will fight in the ring.

117
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:07,880
Whoever's slave wins, wins the bet.

118
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,120
You.

119
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:17,400
I choose her.

120
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,160
Wait, isn't this just a fight?

121
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,480
Since it is a fight,

122
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,600
it must be to the death.

123
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:32,159
Only one person leaves this ring alive.

124
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,080
Wait!

125
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,720
I forfeit!

126
00:07:57,080 --> 00:07:57,720
No!

127
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,360
No! Don't!

128
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:06,080
Didn't I say I forfeit?

129
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:06,920
Sister!

130
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,600
Sister!

131
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:13,000
I lost. What do you want?

132
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,880
I want the Bai Family Army token.

133
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,040
Say that again?

134
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:18,960
The Bai Family Army was disbanded by imperial decree.

135
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:19,640
Young Marquis Bai,

136
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:21,840
what's the use of keeping that token?

137
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:24,440
No. That's a keepsake from my father.

138
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,020
It doesn't matter.

139
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:27,880
In that case,

140
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,160
I'll take a step back.

141
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,520
I just bet

142
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,039
this entire Linglong Pavilion.

143
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,720
It's worth at least 300,000 taels.

144
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:36,640
For the sake of Young Marquis Bai,

145
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:38,440
I'll give you a discount.

146
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,700
200,000 taels.

147
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:42,840
200,000 taels? You might as well rob me!

148
00:08:43,679 --> 00:08:46,480
My games are always fair.

149
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:50,170
If Young Marquis Bai is unwilling,

150
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,410
then stay here and be my mute slave.

151
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:56,280
Young Master Bai, accept your loss.

152
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:58,920
Have you decided?

153
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,160
I'll stay.

154
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,640
How much did he lose?

155
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,120
A mere 200,000 taels.

156
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,960
Miss Song, please go easy on me.

157
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:26,160
If Young Master Bai cannot repay the 200,000 taels he owes me,

158
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:29,040
he will have to become a servant at our Linglong Pavilion.

159
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:29,640
I am teaching you a lesson.

160
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:30,800
Are you unconvinced?

161
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,720
Of course I am.

162
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:34,920
If you dare to run again,

163
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,720
You...

164
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,360
Can you be reasonable?

165
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,400
The money you owe

166
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:41,080
is the hard-earned money your father traded his injuries for.

167
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:44,080
I will go back and ask my father for punishment myself.

168
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,240
Bai Manchuan will repay what he owes.

169
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,600
But please give us a few days.

170
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:50,480
Fine. Then for the sake of the Marquis Zhongyi Manor,

171
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,680
and the General's Manor, I will agree.

172
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:04,010
Does Young Master Bai blame me for being too heavy-handed just now?

173
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,680
I know you were trying to save me.

174
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:06,400
Then why did you...

175
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,120
If I hadn't been heavy-handed,

176
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:10,480
do you think you could have left the gambling house safely?

177
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,640
That is true.

178
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,680
You little brat!

179
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,880
You actually lost 200,000 taels!

180
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,460
How long will it take me to save that much?

181
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,160
I will beat you to death!

182
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:23,280
You are not my son!

183
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:23,720
Stop hitting me, Father.

184
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,050
I will beat you to death!

185
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:30,000
I will bear the consequences of my own actions.

186
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:32,400
At worst, I will sell myself to Baihua Tower to pay the debt.

187
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:34,320
You, you, you...

188
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,720
Father.

189
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,960
I can only help you this far.

190
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,320
Father, Father, Father!

191
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,720
The only plan now is...

192
00:10:45,720 --> 00:10:46,600
is...

193
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,840
for us to get married sooner

194
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:50,170
and use my dowry to pay your gambling debt.

195
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,900
Wouldn't that make me a man who lives off a woman?

196
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:56,200
But it is a good idea.

197
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,660
But gambling is gambling.

198
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:58,480
As long as you gamble,

199
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,720
you must be punished.
